{"tid":2077633,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葛珮帆：外國違反國安法會判死刑 香港最重都係「得10年咋」？ 譚耀宗：會反映","createTime":"2020-06-24T12:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T02:56:02.000Z","uid":212626,"like":35,"dislike":230,"uniUserReply":109,"replies":[{"pid":"c3e107c5ddbe68a4323428b87f20f84dccce71f5","tid":2077633,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:09:32.000Z","msg":"國安法草案說明未有列明刑罰，但譚耀宗當日解畫時曾指「輕則3年、重則10年」，民建聯葛珮帆認為：「最重都係10年咋？外國好勁㗎喎，死刑都有喎，當然香港唔會話鼓吹死刑喇」；<span style=\"color: red;\">譚耀宗回應時則指，國安法的量刑起點是5年，而最高刑期是10年，但刑期尚未最終決定；對於在場建制派嘉賓要求「加辣」，譚稱會向中央反映</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200624/6JDOGAXOTCYM5XMRSV7TX7EQAI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2F6JDOGAXOTCYM5XMRSV7TX7EQAI%2F&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPreFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=51991e63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2F6JDOGAXOTCYM5XMRSV7TX7EQAI%2F&h=0bde8343\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200624/6JDOGAXOTCYM5XMRSV7TX7EQAI/</a><br />\n死刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1c2d49f1406183cbd264107afd4860a7d7b454","tid":2077633,"uid":21545,"like":119,"dislike":1,"score":118,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:10:27.000Z","msg":"問題係而家黨國不分<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001fc43468b97e7d359329dd1ea03b1ba91c53cb","tid":2077633,"uid":54721,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:12:24.000Z","msg":"作法自斃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288d0611d83e83ebdf5886d2ff8bb3757a305af0","tid":2077633,"uid":201374,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:12:28.000Z","msg":"外國有民主"},{"pid":"0feda39e7b08523dd7d82638d89a96e95c2acfc4","tid":2077633,"uid":17796,"like":95,"dislike":1,"score":94,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:14:49.000Z","msg":"假博士似乎好想死先